                    }
                  }
                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "#doi:10.1103/PhysRevC.100.064002"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "SYNCH"
                ],
                "institute": "2JPNKEK"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " BL05 Low-Divergence beam branch in",
                "MLF at J-PARC"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "SPALL"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The pulsed neutron beams are produced by the",
                "spallation process at the MLF in J-PARC.",
                "Peak energy was 11.7 meV at the time of measurement.",
                "The proton beam power was approximately 410 kW."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Natural noble gas (He, Ar, Kr and Xe) was used as",
                "target and Ne gas was used as a monitor material.",
                "The gas was filled in an aluminum target cell with",
                "a diameter of 50 mm and a length of 150 mm giving it",
                "a volume of about 300 cm3.",
                "The gas was pressurized to approximately 1.85 atm and",
                "the pressure and temperature was monitored",
                "continuously throughout each run."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PS",
                "PROPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Neutrons scattered by the target gas were",
                "detected by a 3He-gas-filled position sensitive",
                "detector (3He PSD).",
                "The 3He PSD contained seven proportional counter tubes",
                "each with a diameter of 12.7 mm covering an area",
                "600 mm wide and 90 mm high."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "-Acquire angular and energy-dependent scattering data",
                " for target gases and Ne."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The neutron count rate was measured separately for",
                "each gas species and for the empty cell.",
                "Empty-cell data are subtracted from that of",
                "the gas-filled cell and normalized by the number",
                "density and the proton beam power at MLF.",
                "Form the ratios of the results of target gases (He, Ar,",
                "Kr and Xe) with respect to that of Ne.",
                "Perform a Monte Carlo simulation in order to correct",
                "the differences of angular distribution of scattered",
                "neutrons between the target gases and Ne.",
                "Using the experimental event rates of the target gases",
                "relative to the measured Ne data and scattering cross",
                "sections of Ne, scattering cross section of the target",
                "gases were deduced.",
                "The free atom cross sections were calculated from the",
                "deduced bound atom cross sections."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "In the analysis,",
                "-Statistical uncertainty in the experiments",
                "-Systematic uncertainties due to pressure and",
                " temperature stability",
                "-Systematic uncertainties due to pressure dependence of",
                " cell geometry (negligibly small),",
                "-Systematic uncertainties due to multiple scattering",
                " (<0.1%)",
                "-Uncertainty in the simulation",
                "were discussed."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
